  "summary": "Improper Restriction of XML External Entity Reference in Plone",
  "details": "Plone before 5.2.3 allows XXE attacks via a feature that is protected by an unapplied permission of plone.schemaeditor.ManageSchemata (therefore, only available to the Manager role).",
